  , bug #292340

*barry-0.16 (18 Oct 2009)

  18 Oct 2009; Víctor Ostorga <vostorga@gentoo.org>
  +files/10-blackberry.rules, -barry-0.8.ebuild, -barry-0.9.ebuild,
